  "description": "So as I settle into Obsidian and prepare for the long slog of bringing in old content - and adding new content - I wondered if there were any good plugins for gamifying Obsidian. I actually got inspired because I saw, while importing 2023-11-14, Winter Orientation, that I wrote that using 4theWords, a gamifying online writng platform.\nWell, a Web search turned up a few that seemed of interest, right away.\n",
